subject: NCAA Basketball Championships (Men)
Basketball (College)
lead_paragraph: Norfolk State toppled Missouri and became the first 15th seed since Hampton in 1991 to knock off a No. 2 seed, and only the fifth since 1985. Later, Lehigh became the sixth.
